a.n: Ingrid & Lola - Road to Manta Corridor

p.k: In Paris, Louis Manta, the shampoo specialist of a hair salon is missing. His bosscalls Lola Jost (Muriel Robin) and Ingrid Diesel (Anne Le Nen) to the rescue. The investigators travel through the Parisian underworld and towards the South Seas and the dangerous reefs of Manta Corridor.
